        <p>
          We cancel a common factor of <var name="$c"/> as follows:
          <me>
            \frac{\overset{<var name="$a"/>}{\cancel{<var name="$top"/>}}}{\underset{<var name="$b"/>}{\cancel{<var name="$bottom"/>}}}=\frac{<var name="$a"/>}{<var name="$b"/>}
          </me>
        </p>
